Welcome to Super Planet! We develop and publish games for mobile devices.
By clicking or tapping the button indicating the acceptance of these Terms, or by using the Game Services, you will be agreed to the processing of the Data (including Personal Information) with the terms of this Terms of Use Policy.
This Privacy Policy describes the ways we collect, store, use, and disclose the information, including personal information, and data that our users provide or we collect in connection with any Super Planet games provided on a mobile platform. Additionally, this policy describes your rights and choices concerning your information. Please note that this private policy may be modified or be updated.
Information and Data We Collect from You
We collect information you choose to provide or give us in any manner. You don’t have to share information when we ask you for it, but if you decline, you might not be able to access certain Super Planet services, or take advantage of their full functionality.
In order to provide 5 years (from the date the user starts using our services to the date of withdrawal) of game and customer services for our game users, we will be collecting information as below:
1)
Information that will be collected to provide game service
Player’s name
Type of OS (Android, iOS, etc.)
ID used in different platforms (Google Games, Apple Game Center)
Language of users
Game history
Devices in use (iPhone, Galaxy, Sony, etc.)
2)
Information that will be collected to provide a more accurate and prompt service
Game Version (ex. v1.0.3, etc.)
Version of OS (AOS, iOS)
Unique device identification number (This will be mainly used to help you when you lose your account.)
3)
Information that we collect from third parties
We may obtain information from third parties to use along with the information we collect. We can receive information from third-party platforms (ex. Google Play, App Store, Facebook) if you download the Super Planet games or link your game account to your demanded platform.
We may partner with third parties such as payment gateway companies, platform service companies, and analytic companies to gather advertising and analytics information to help support our marketing initiatives, improve Super Planet services, and better manage our ad campaigns. We may share your Personal Information with these third party service providers so that they may provide their services to us.
If you don’t want to take advantage of the services that the third-party analytics and advertising companies provide on the Super Planet services, you may be able to opt-out of some of them by visiting
http://www.aboutads.info
or
http://www.networkadvertising.org/choices/
, or
https://www.youronlinechoices.com/
.
Please note that opting-out of interest-based advertising won’t necessarily entirely prevent information from being collected automatically on the Super Planet services, and it doesn’t mean you will receive fewer ads or stop them from being displayed. Instead, the ads you do receive won’t be interest-based any longer and therefore might be less relevant to your interests.
Method of Collection
We can collect information in the following ways.
Homepage
Mobile
Written form
Membership
Membership information modification
Community
E-mail
